-------------------------------------------------------
Package to calculate synthetic stellar spectra and SSPs
-------------------------------------------------------

**** RUNNING TESTS --> USE ANOTHER DIRECTORY ****

Before running the scripts, use python script:

  > link.py

to create symbolic links to the following files:
  - absoru2.dat
  - atoms.dat**  
  - grid.mod
  - hmap.dat
  - molecules.dat
  - partit.dat

(link.py --> see https://trevisanj.github.io/PFANT/ AND https://trevisanj.github.io/pyfant/)

** atoms.dat --> USE THE ONE IN THIS DIRECTORY INSTEAD
     > ln -s ../SSP_package_PFANTnew/atoms.dat atoms.dat

****************************************
IN SUMMARY, IN YOUR TEST DIRECTORY, DO:
****************************************
  > link.py
  > rm atoms.dat
  > ln -s ../SSP_package_PFANTnew/atoms.dat atoms.dat
  > cp -r ../SSP_package_PFANTnew/* .  
  

 
